      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing direct mechanical linkage to the rear-mounted limited-slip differential. The chassis has been inspected with rear subframe reinforcement already addressed, ensuring structural rigidity during spirited cornering. The suspension retains its factory-tuned balance with MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, offering precise feedback through the rack-and-pinion steering. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While the aesthetic reflects honest use, the powertrain and drivetrain remain in excellent operational health for the discerning purist.",
