    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a perfect balance of luxury and daily reliability. The exterior is finished in a Deep Obsidian Black that retains a deep, mirror-like gloss; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front hood consistent with careful highway use, the body is straight and free of any major dents or scratches. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of cream leather and polished walnut trim. The upholstery is supple and intact, showing only light softening on the driver's side bolster, and all electronic components\u2014including the premium surround-sound system and heated seats\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a full service history. We recently performed a comprehensive inspection, resulting in new brake pads and a fresh synthetic oil change. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. The tires are matching Continentals with plenty of tread depth remaining. Aside from a small curb scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel, this vehicle presents beautifully and is ready for immediate enjoyment.",
